    <section class="home-lead">
        <h2>Micro Focus Careers</h2>
        <!--begin tabbed content-->
            <ul id="tabs">
    <li class="active">Our Careers</li>
    <li>Diversity</li>
    <li>Graduates and Careers</li>
    <li>Benefits and Culture</li>
</ul>
<ul id="tab">
    <li class="active careers-tab">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KFmd2XizZz0?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <div>
            <p class="larger-text">Micro Focus understands the success of our work depends on the quality of the people we ask to do it. From the back-end office through to sales and support, if we are to thrive and survive in a fiercely-competitive marketplace, then we need the best-in-class staff for every area.</p>
            <p>That is why we offer the packages of rewards and benefits needed to attract and retain the best industry talent. Then we put in place the structures that help our people flourish, develop and take our company forward.</p>
            <p>Micro Focus is a big operation. More than 4,000 people are at work at 100 locations across the globe. Whether you are helping to make, sell or support our great software, or assist the people who do, you will be in great company.</p>
            <p>At Micro Focus, we make software and build careers.</p>
        </div>
    </li>
    <!--end Our Careers tab-->
    
    <li>
        <p class="larger-text">"Taking our Customers into Tomorrow"</p>
        <p>Micro Focus strives as an organization to reflect the globally diverse audience that our software serves. Diverse perspectives, ideas and cultural benefits are critical to the development of quality products and services.</p>
        <p>Micro Focus fosters diversity through recruiting outreach programs, community based career fairs, university career centers and internships, and graduate student programs.</p>
    </li>
    <!--end Diversity tab-->
    
    <li>
        <p class="larger-text">Talented software developers are the heart of our business at Micro Focus. The graduate programme is a great way to start your career with Micro Focus, and comes with a competitive starting package. You will be guided by a mentor who will support your progress as your career develops. You will also have the opportunity to work in different teams to explore various technical challenges, or you may choose to specialize in one area.   Our development teams include some of the industry’s most gifted and original minds, and we enjoy a great team spirit in a relaxed, yet professional goal-oriented atmosphere working on a very broad range of technologies.</p>
        <p>Our current graduates voted via the JobCrowd (UK’s leading graduate job review website) and placed Micro Focus in the Top 10 IT and Telecommunication companies for IT graduates to work for, with nearly 5/5 stars.</p>
    </li>
    <!--end Graduates and Careers tab-->
    
    <li>
        <h3>Focused on Customer Success</h3>

        <p>Micro Focus has a culture of listening and learning, where colleagues work as one: supporting each other, holding each other accountable, and providing fast, flawless execution. Our number one mission is our customers’ successes.</p>
        
        <p>We value a productive workplace where colleagues treat each other with respect, integrity, honesty, and openness.  The principles of the Micro Focus Professional Charter reinforce our actions on a daily basis:</p>
        
        <h4>Collaborate for success</h4>
        
        <p>As a team, we work together across functions and geographies in support of each opportunity. We focus on customer needs and success. We celebrate our successes.</p>
        
        <h4>Close the communications loop</h4>
        
        <p>Act upon requests and seek feedback to continually improve processes and customer satisfaction.</p>
        
        <h4>Respond promptly</h4>
        
        <p>Responding fast and flawlessly leads to superb customer satisfaction for internal and external customers.</p>
        
        <h4>Deliver on commitments</h4>
        
        <p>We build trust and respect with our customers through high quality and timely delivery.</p>
        
        <h4>Take responsibility & initiative</h4>
        
        <p>Colleagues are empowered to make a change within the organization.</p>
        
        <h4>Get involved, debate passionately, get on board</h4>
        
        <p>Be open, be involved, embrace change and be part of creating a successful organization.</p>
    </li>
    <!--end Benefits and Culture tab-->
</ul>

        <!-- end tabbed content -->
